adwaita-icon-theme
________________________________________________________________________________

Mostly private use system icons. [0]

Upstream: https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/adwaita-icon-theme


[000] Index
________________________________________________________________________________

* Installation ........................................................... [001]
